Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 这个童话故事的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在21世纪早期 作为现实的技术具体化出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.65,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2030年前后爆发的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴随着气温急剧下降 粮食不足加剧恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕着能源资源的争夺不断发生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2045年 爆发了持续20年的第3次世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人口急减到30亿人以下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争之所以没成为热核战争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.59,0:00:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为全世界的魔法师团结一致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后到21世纪末
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不稳定的情势下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各国开始争先培养魔法师了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身为魔神 兄长大人踏上了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅只是为了我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.41,0:01:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底要怎么报答兄长大人才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回报什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连我如今的生命也是兄长大人给予的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:51.35,Comment,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.64,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,入学式的彩排马上就要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.76,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,请相关人员到礼堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全无法认同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么兄长大人是替补生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入学测试的成绩 兄长大人明明是第一名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来不应该由我 是由兄长大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里比起笔试 还是魔法实技更为重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是替补 我居然能考上一高…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要说这种没有霸气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论学习还是体术 明明没有人能胜过你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是魔法 兄长大人要是用全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是说出来那也无济于事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在非常抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你代替我生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有这份心意我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都是被你所救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人一直都在谴责我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有骗人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你为我着想那样 我也一直把你放在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人 你这样说「放在心里什么的」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉她好像有点误会了 不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 即使你辞退新生致词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为二科生的我也不可能代替你被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪慧的你应该能明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有啊 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我这个没用哥哥看看可爱妹妹的风光模样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人并不是什么没用的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我刚才讲出那么任性的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人 请欣赏我的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 接下来要怎样消磨时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国立魔法大学附属高中第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了培养魔法技能师的国策机关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考上这所高中 也就说明是在魔法上得到证明的菁英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在这所高中里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说那个人不是杂草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(512,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然这么早就来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是替补 还这么有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是新生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么需要我帮忙的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一科生的学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CAD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 我是学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫七草真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数字的七 花草的草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含数家系…而且还是七草啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫…不 本人叫司波达也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波达也学弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 原来你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长！彩排要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们谈话中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面一半是花冠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(497,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面一半是杂草
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(497,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差别意识最为强烈的 就是受到差别对待的人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你旁边有人坐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我叫柴田美月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带眼镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫司波达也 我才是请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是千叶艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多指教 司波同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这真的可以说是一个有趣的巧合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么巧合？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 司波 柴田 千叶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有点谐音的感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千叶吗 又是含数家系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.19,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真亏你能察觉到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:55.11,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,司波 柴田 千叶 司波 柴田 千叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么现在国立魔法大学附属高中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一高中入学式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.77,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着新生致词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新生代表 司波深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在柔和的阳光沐浴下 新生的樱花漫天飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蓓蕾初绽春天里的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能就读名门国立魔法大学附属高中 第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到非常喜悦 还倍受光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表所有新生 怀着作为第一高中一员的荣誉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同学 接下来要不要去看一下教室？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我和妹妹有约了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个你的妹妹难道是新生代表的司波深雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们是双胞胎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然经常会被问 但不是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是4月出生 妹妹是3月出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你居然能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 与其说是气氛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说你们两位散发出的氛围非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女生 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能看出氛围 你真有一双好眼睛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵子放射光过敏症
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再被继续看下去很危险 我的秘密会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.06,0:08:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午好 又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 兄长大人 你马上就要去约会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会这样啊 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两位是我的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种说法非常失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫司波深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫柴田美月 我才是请你多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是千叶艾莉卡 叫我艾莉卡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以叫你深雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪你其实是很直爽的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 学生会各位的要事已经完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天只是想打声招呼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细节就改天再谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波学弟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改天一定要好好谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人十分抱歉 都是因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 两位…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人 我现在帮你冲咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方才那些人打电话过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了些祝贺入学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是父亲和小百合小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是他们有对兄长大人说什么吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一如既往什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果连一封邮件都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一时失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无视爸爸要我去公司帮忙的命令决定升学的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这当作是器重我 你就不会生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人这样说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 请你不要隐藏气息潜行过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我是潜行者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏气息对我来说就是天性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经没有忍者这种职业了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是忍者　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是继承了血统的潜行者 忍术使用者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道老师您是历史悠久古式魔法的正统继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是您也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是第一高中的校服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 昨天就是入学式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天是来向您报告我们入学的消息的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崭新的校服洋溢着清纯的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀丽的外表下难以掩盖内部的美色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是含苞待放的花蕾 刚刚萌发的新芽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这就是萌 这简直太萌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 深雪感到有些畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您能冷静一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛 达也 居然背后袭击我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定光凭体术我已经不及达也你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 让你的裙子沾上泥土了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我的衣服都整理了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.80,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小事不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 兄长大人要吃早饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师您如果不介意的话也请尝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同学你在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在确认课程和注册听课
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我只是很惊讶现在还有只用键盘输入的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果习惯的话这样反而更快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫西城雷欧赫特 叫我雷欧就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅长的是收束系的硬化魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫司波达也 叫我达也就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 达也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 你擅长什么魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不擅长实际操作 我的目标是做一个魔法工程技师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 你确实看起来脑袋不错的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 司波同学你打算做魔法工程技师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达也 这家伙是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就叫人“这家伙” 真是个失礼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不招人喜欢的男生就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.94,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 失礼的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为脸长得还算不错就可以随便乱说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表可是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.52,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你这种把邋遢当成奔放的恶心男生是不会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧 算了吧 打预备铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉卡你也说得有点过分了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么老师会来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参观工作室还真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目标也是魔法工程技师 真是学到了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么复杂的工作我行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定没戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 话说你跟我们一起吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在跟美月还有司波同学一起吃饭而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跟你们一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 这边有位子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波深雪 是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫司波…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起去宽敞点的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰他们多不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 我就在这里就行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司波同学 最好别跟杂草坐在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(486,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一科和二科最好划清界限哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 我已经先吃完了就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 达也 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达也同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也差不多也该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有事找她商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,就是 我们只是想打扰她一会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必为此道歉 深雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 深雪同学说过要跟她哥哥一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有什么权利拆散他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月在说什么呢 瞎误会什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深雪 你紧张什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我没有紧张哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你为什么突然用疑问句式？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们1-A之间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂草别插嘴我们花冠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(291,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(498,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不都是新生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些花冠现在能比我们优秀多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,437)\fs21}Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道我们有多优秀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请你一定展示给我们看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那就展示给你们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是才能的差距！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种距离还是体术比较快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你刚才连我的手也打算一起打下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会那么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别打算敷衍过去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是些杂草
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(481,437)\fs21}Weed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗香？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 自卫目的之外的对人魔法攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在违反校规之前已经违反法律了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是风纪委员会委员长渡边摩利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我相关事宜 你们全部跟我走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的小玩笑开得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们听说森崎家的「迅发」很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以后的学习打算让他给我们演示看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们逼得太紧 不自觉就出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个女生想要做出攻击性魔法又怎么解释？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是个闪光魔法 而且还抑制了很多威力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你能分析展开的魔法启动式嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太擅长实际操作 但是很擅长分析
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.17,0:21:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像也很擅长掩饰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么敢掩饰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是个二科生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国立魔法大学附属高中第一高中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能考上这所高中 也就说明是在魔法上得到证明的菁英
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是在这所高中里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从入学开始 就已经存在优等生和劣等生了
